import React from 'react'
import styles from '../styles/AddForm.module.css'

function AddForm() {
  
  const submitHandler = e => {
    e.preventDefault()
    
  }
  return (
      <form onSubmit={submitHandler}>
        <label>Team's Name:</label>
        <input type="text"/>
        <label>Team's City:</label>
        <input type="text"/>
        <label>Team's State:</label>
        <input type="text"/>
        <label>Team's Stadium:</label>
        <input type="text"/>
        <label>Team's Picture:</label>
        <input type="text"/>
        <button>Submit</button>
      </form>
  )
}

export default AddForm
